        "execSummary":  "The A2A gateway pattern described here solves one of the most pressing enterprise multi-agent challenges: how to securely manage, discover, and control inter-agent communication as the number of deployed agents scales. The centralized single-domain entry point with fine-grained JWT scoping is a practical answer to the governance vacuum that often accompanies rapid agent proliferation in enterprises. For AI platform and operations leaders, this architecture is a reference model for building observable, auditable agent networks that satisfy enterprise security requirements without custom-building every integration. The Terraform IaC templates and hybrid/multi-cloud deployment guidance lower the barrier to adopting this pattern across existing AWS environments.",
