        "execSummary":  "Organizations moving from AI pilots to production now compete on cost-per-token efficiency rather than raw compute specs, and NVIDIA\u0027s full-stack inference software is reshaping that equation. Dramatic performance improvementsΓÇöup to 5x in a single month for models like DeepSeek V4ΓÇöare being driven by software codesigned with Blackwell hardware, not just silicon advances. The open-source flywheel accelerates this further: production deployments feed optimizations back into shared frameworks, enabling frontier models to have day-zero deployment recipes. For enterprise budget owners, this signals that infrastructure vendor lock-in decisions made today will have compounding cost implications as AI workloads scale.",
