        "execSummary":  "This initiative redefines what enterprise AI vendor support looks likeΓÇömoving from advisory consulting to embedded human-AI hybrid delivery teams with hard outcome timelines. The 45-day sprint model creates accountability structures that traditional professional services engagements lack, and the knowledge-graph residual means value compounds after the engagement ends rather than walking out the door with the consultants. For customer-support leaders evaluating AWS partnerships, this signals AWS is competing on speed-to-production, not just infrastructure capability. The $1B commitment also signals AWS views enterprise AI deployment bottlenecksΓÇönot model capabilityΓÇöas the primary competitive battleground for the next 18-24 months.",
